hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377bbf701308be79d14f8c4b8e170ffa0321f710","tid":114300,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"訓前講句早抖<br />\n起身講句早晨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想每日都人咁對我"},{"pid":"f62ba893490b0b213b3fd136fdef4b3b69941aaa","tid":114300,"uid":37752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓前講句早抖<br />\n起身講句早晨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想每日都人咁對我</blockquote><br />\n講又點，咪又係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986f0facc64f1038fbd01b3e123103020795df1c","tid":114300,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓前講句早抖<br />\n起身講句早晨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想每日都人咁對我</blockquote><br />\n講又點，咪又係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男女朋友又點 咪又係會失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92f4ab645639c1804ac901d5e7f8e866c778043","tid":114300,"uid":36414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畀D空間對方係咪真係咁難</blockquote><br />\n翻工個陣冇應機 <br />\n放工岀現一陣<br />\n到夜晚食飯冇應機<br />\n講幾句就去沖涼<br />\n之後岀現一陣又消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇chur佢 只係單方面期待<br />\n仲有冇咩做得唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有D人唔會長期拎住部機, 我就係果種人<br />\n<br />\n返工食飯, 唔係話完全唔會應, 不過專心返工, 食飯同家人朋友交流吓好正常啫<br />\n有時想專心做下自己野, 睇套戲, 睇套劇, 打下機, 中間唔會應到你, 時間又好快過<br />\n<br />\n你又話冇chur佢, 但樓上又話同男友講過唔咁樣會唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d0ae508840f3175f4f33bfdfaf127a586ca43d","tid":114300,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畀D空間對方係咪真係咁難</blockquote><br />\n翻工個陣冇應機 <br />\n放工岀現一陣<br />\n到夜晚食飯冇應機<br />\n講幾句就去沖涼<br />\n之後岀現一陣又消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇chur佢 只係單方面期待<br />\n仲有冇咩做得唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有D人唔會長期拎住部機, 我就係果種人<br />\n<br />\n返工食飯, 唔係話完全唔會應, 不過專心返工, 食飯同家人朋友交流吓好正常啫<br />\n有時想專心做下自己野, 睇套戲, 睇套劇, 打下機, 中間唔會應到你, 時間又好快過<br />\n<br />\n你又話冇chur佢, 但樓上又話同男友講過唔咁樣會唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初初一齊個陣講過一次 <br />\n之後都係經常突然失蹤 都冇再拎岀黎講<br />\n收埋sad咪算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b867adad3ede35f202f797365de33ce6daa8dc3","tid":114300,"uid":69844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:17:17.000Z","msg":"早抖"},{"pid":"40f606d9c0ff55ce76377e21cf9c7683403f8ee2","tid":114300,"uid":66126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"有你依啲女人真係痴線 俾啲空間男人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e319957783119b3dfb3a0392fd6f21ae2cb0ea5b","tid":114300,"uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:01:38.000Z","msg":"其實講早晨早唞係一種安全感黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0877d85197d3eea12d9d300216f28d30a391be","tid":114300,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:11:15.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4568c4df556d483a3a08dd8